{"tid":1941453,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[支那病毒] 馬德里逾千人病亡 溜冰場改為臨時停屍間","createTime":"2020-03-24T12:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T12:13:05.000Z","uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fcd1818a3651c99abadc139bbaa2f23711ad52d2","tid":1941453,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T12:13:05.000Z","msg":"西班牙疫情在歐洲國家中僅次於意大利，首都馬德里是重災區，死亡人數達逾1,200人，佔全國總數約一半，一個溜冰場將用作臨時停屍間。<br />\n<br />\n市立殯儀館由於器材不足，周二起暫停接收遺體。市政廳表示，「冰宮」商場（Palacio de Hielo）已表示願意提供商場內那個面積1,800平方米、達奧運標準的溜冰場，作臨時殮房。地方政府和軍方將協助安排。<br />\n<br />\n溜冰場附近的IFEMA會議中心，已改成武漢肺炎臨時醫院，本周可收1,300名病人，126人已經入院。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙全國確診宗數逾3.3萬，僅次於中國、意大利、美國，2,182人死亡。<br />\n<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200324/3NUBP6VH7HXLO5U7CK6WZ7UMBQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3wTGDdCdZBj2AWhcQcyJ9Ayq8ah5I62RxGZyComDJdAfz55I4f7xXksbI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200324%2F3NUBP6VH7HXLO5U7CK6WZ7UMBQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3wTGDdCdZBj2AWhcQcyJ9Ayq8ah5I62RxGZyComDJdAfz55I4f7xXksbI&d=Afoh3Yf6cz19ESyehd0SJ7ZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=9ad9ed2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200324%2F3NUBP6VH7HXLO5U7CK6WZ7UMBQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR3wTGDdCdZBj2AWhcQcyJ9Ayq8ah5I62RxGZyComDJdAfz55I4f7xXksbI&h=8fd865f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200324/3NUBP6VH7HXLO5U7CK6WZ7UMBQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR3wTGDdCdZBj2AWhcQcyJ9Ayq8ah5I62RxGZyCo